It was not long before, fireflies became a rare sight in urban parks, but recently in Jiulong Wetland Park in Lishui City, east China's Zhejiang Province, fireflies have come back. A great amount of fireflies has lighten up the night, creating a fantasy world for the citizens. As the environment has improved in recent years, so has the increase in the population of the fireflies. (All images via CFP) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)